engChrName: This here will be the turning point! All units, assume the Dual Lancer formation!
engSearchText:
This here will be the turning point! All units,
assume the Dual Lancer formation!
jpnChrName: ここが分け目だ── 総員、戦形を《双槍騎兵（ドッペルランツェレイター）》へ！
jpnSearchText:
ここが分け目だ──
総員、戦形を《双槍騎兵（ドッペルランツェレイター）》へ！

engChrName: Ja!
engSearchText: Ja!
jpnChrName: Ｊａ（ヤー）！！
jpnSearchText: Ｊａ（ヤー）！！

engChrName: We won't be defeated! Shine, Falcons of the Sun!
engSearchText:
We won't be defeated! Shine, Falcons of
the Sun!
jpnChrName: 我らも行くぞ──！ 赫（かがや）け、《太陽の鷹（エル＝アルコン）》の戦翼！
jpnSearchText:
我らも行くぞ──！
赫（かがや）け、《太陽の鷹（エル＝アルコン）》の戦翼！

engChrName: Sir!
engSearchText: Sir!
jpnChrName: 応（ウーラ）！！
jpnSearchText: 応（ウーラ）！！

engChrName: Regimental commander of the Eisenschild, Geraint Reigar!
engSearchText:
Regimental commander of the Eisenschild,
Geraint Reigar!
jpnChrName: 《アイゼンシルト》連隊長、 ゲラント・レイガー殿！
jpnSearchText:
《アイゼンシルト》連隊長、
ゲラント・レイガー殿！

engChrName: We are open to accepting your offer for a ceasefire! How does a 7:3 split sound?
engSearchText:
We are open to accepting your offer for a
ceasefire! How does a 7:3 split sound?
jpnChrName: 停戦の申し出を受け入れる！ ７：３ならばどうだ！？
jpnSearchText:
停戦の申し出を受け入れる！
７：３ならばどうだ！？

engChrName: Vice Chief of the Warriors of Kruga, Hasan Al-Fayed!
engSearchText:
Vice Chief of the Warriors of Kruga,
Hasan Al-Fayed!
jpnChrName: 《クルガ戦士団》副頭目、 ハサン・アルファイド殿！
jpnSearchText:
《クルガ戦士団》副頭目、
ハサン・アルファイド殿！

engChrName: We will accept no less than 6:4! Fail to accept, and the fighting continues!
engSearchText:
We will accept no less than 6:4! Fail to
accept, and the fighting continues!
jpnChrName: ６：４が条件だ！ 退かなければ続行する！
jpnSearchText:
６：４が条件だ！
退かなければ続行する！

engChrName: Very well! 6:4 to us it is!
engSearchText: Very well! 6:4 to us it is!
jpnChrName: ──いいだろう！ ６：４で我らの勝利だ！
jpnSearchText:
──いいだろう！
６：４で我らの勝利だ！

engChrName: Glory to the Kruga! Glory to Arusha!
engSearchText: Glory to the Kruga! Glory to Arusha!
jpnChrName: クルガに焔と翼の女神（アルーシャ）の栄光あれ！！
jpnSearchText: クルガに焔と翼の女神（アルーシャ）の栄光あれ！！

engChrName: YEEEAH!
engSearchText: YEEEAH!
jpnChrName: おおおおおおおっ……！
jpnSearchText: おおおおおおおっ……！

engChrName: *pant* *pant*
engSearchText: *pant* *pant*
jpnChrName: はあっ、はあっ……
jpnSearchText: はあっ、はあっ……

engChrName: That works, I guess. I figured more it was gonna end in a draw.
engSearchText:
That works, I guess. I figured more it was gonna end
in a draw.
jpnChrName: やれやれ、相討ちに 持ち込まれるかと思ったが……
jpnSearchText:
やれやれ、相討ちに
持ち込まれるかと思ったが……

engChrName: Your counterattack was really good—just lacking that bit of oomph at the end.
engSearchText:
Your counterattack was really good—just lacking that
bit of oomph at the end.
jpnChrName: ──さっきの反撃（カウンター）は良かったけど、 ちょいと詰めが甘かったね？
jpnSearchText:
──さっきの反撃（カウンター）は良かったけど、
ちょいと詰めが甘かったね？

engChrName: If you'd seen my attempt to throw you off balance coming, you'd've had a slew of more strategic options to work with.
engSearchText:
If you'd seen my attempt to throw you off balance
coming, you'd've had a slew of more strategic options
to work with.
jpnChrName: アタシの撹乱を想定しておけば ここぞの選択肢も広げられただろう。
jpnSearchText:
アタシの撹乱を想定しておけば
ここぞの選択肢も広げられただろう。

engChrName: *pant* *pant* You're... You're right.
engSearchText: *pant* *pant* You're... You're right.
jpnChrName: はあっ、はあっ…… ……やっぱり……そうですよね……
jpnSearchText:
はあっ、はあっ……
……やっぱり……そうですよね……

engChrName: Thanks...*pant*...Aida.
engSearchText: Thanks...*pant*...Aida.
jpnChrName: はあはあ…… ありがとう……アイーダさん。
jpnSearchText:
はあはあ……
ありがとう……アイーダさん。

engChrName: Think nothing of it. You've got a lot of potential— you just need more practice and to up your stamina.
engSearchText:
Think nothing of it. You've got a lot of potential—
you just need more practice and to up your stamina.
jpnChrName: フフ、アンタはもっと伸びる。 今は体力と手数を増やしときな。
jpnSearchText:
フフ、アンタはもっと伸びる。
今は体力と手数を増やしときな。

engChrName: With enough of both, you'll be right on the heels of my other little sister from back in the day in no time.
engSearchText:
With enough of both, you'll be right on the heels of
my other little sister from back in the day in no time.
jpnChrName: そうすりゃアタシの 昔の妹分にだって届くだろうさ。
jpnSearchText:
そうすりゃアタシの
昔の妹分にだって届くだろうさ。

engChrName: Do you mean Sylphid?
engSearchText: Do you mean Sylphid?
jpnChrName: あ…… “妖精”って人ですよね。
jpnSearchText:
あ……
“妖精”って人ですよね。

engChrName: I'd still like to know more about her.
engSearchText: I'd still like to know more about her.
jpnChrName: ……ちょっと気になる、かな。
jpnSearchText: ……ちょっと気になる、かな。

engChrName: Oh! Hey! That tickles!
engSearchText: Oh! Hey! That tickles!
jpnChrName: わわっ…… くすぐったいよ、アイーダさん。
jpnSearchText:
わわっ……
くすぐったいよ、アイーダさん。

engChrName: Heehee. I can't help it! I see this hair and I just get the urge to ruffle it.
engSearchText:
Heehee. I can't help it! I see this hair and I just get
the urge to ruffle it.
jpnChrName: いや～、相変わらずいい感触だねぇ。
jpnSearchText: いや～、相変わらずいい感触だねぇ。

engChrName: Hmm... Well, next time we meet off the battlefield, I'll tell you about my old corps.
engSearchText:
Hmm... Well, next time we meet off the battlefield,
I'll tell you about my old corps.
jpnChrName: そうだね……また今度、 戦場以外で会えたら話してあげるよ。
jpnSearchText:
そうだね……また今度、
戦場以外で会えたら話してあげるよ。

engChrName: Zephyr's got a whole lotta stories in it to tell.
engSearchText: Zephyr's got a whole lotta stories in it to tell.
jpnChrName: アタシが前にいた団──《西風》の事を。
jpnSearchText: アタシが前にいた団──《西風》の事を。

engChrName: Awesome! Better make that a promise!
engSearchText: Awesome! Better make that a promise!
jpnChrName: うんっ、約束ですよ……！
jpnSearchText: うんっ、約束ですよ……！

engChrName: Ugh... Not yet!
engSearchText: Ugh... Not yet!
jpnChrName: くっ……まだまだ！
jpnSearchText: くっ……まだまだ！

engChrName: Heh. Too easy!
engSearchText: Heh. Too easy!
jpnChrName: ハッ、甘いね──！
jpnSearchText: ハッ、甘いね──！

engChrName: Ahh!
engSearchText: Ahh!
jpnChrName: ああっ……！？
jpnSearchText: ああっ……！？

engChrName: I've got you!
engSearchText: I've got you!
jpnChrName: ──もらった！
jpnSearchText: ──もらった！

engChrName: O flames...
engSearchText: O flames...
jpnChrName: ッ……焔よ──
jpnSearchText: ッ……焔よ──

engChrName: ...become one with me!
engSearchText: ...become one with me!
jpnChrName: 我が息吹となれ──！！
jpnSearchText: 我が息吹となれ──！！
っ……！？
ぁ…………

engChrName: Well, look at that. Guess we lost this one, huh?
engSearchText: Well, look at that. Guess we lost this one, huh?
jpnChrName: ……やれやれ。 アタシらの負け、か。
jpnSearchText:
……やれやれ。
アタシらの負け、か。
